CLOSEArizona nonprofits are struggling on two fronts during the COVID-19 crisis: Demand for services is increasing while fundraisers are being canceled and volunteers are staying home.
This list of more than 170 Arizona nonprofits includes the following information:Name of organization and how to reach by phone, email or online.
Search by any of those categories or click on the name of each nonprofit to get more information on each.
To add your group to the list, fill out the form found here: https://azcentral.formstack.com/forms/nonprofit_group_listing.
